{"tid":1584172,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（為歷史正名）係革命而非動亂，係起義非作反（連登歷史學家入）","createTime":"2019-09-21T03:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T03:21:27.000Z","uid":201512,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"08ce2bbd506f0a3ad641df92df2bb43806e9b943","tid":1584172,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:33:41.000Z","msg":"「九七回歸」、「新中國成立」，文革「十年浩劫」變成艱辛的探索<br />\n各種各樣共匪詞彙不知不覺早已成為香港人的日常用語，甚至影響緊每一個香港人對一樣歷史事件的睇法。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">接受敵人對事件的定性，就無形中加強呢個非法政權的合法性。</span></span>，呢個係點解我地必須爭取撤回暴動定性。<br />\n<br />\n同樣地，各種各樣帶有共產黨史觀的說法充斥著香港人的思想入面。<br />\n<br />\n呢個po希望將所有香港人常犯的錯誤史觀糾正，對抗共產黨一言堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaea8b18845981442469ed43a3d4378f607018e6","tid":1584172,"uid":201512,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:34:16.000Z","msg":"九七回歸&mdash;&mdash;＞九七淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e933de8a1f5061d7bbccb3e1de50e74ec56f34","tid":1584172,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:35:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"ad2df0f466ce30b238fe2a00994ecffc2aa8a852","tid":1584172,"uid":201512,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:35:34.000Z","msg":"中國<del>收回</del>香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">侵佔</span>"},{"pid":"d54154061e8ed948fcca17ca725fe8c9d040b8ba","tid":1584172,"uid":255105,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:37:04.000Z","msg":"內地＝＞中國<br />\n返大陸＝＞去中國<br />\n中央政府＝＞中國政府<br />\n港英政府＝＞英治政府<br />\n英國殖民統治＝＞英治時期<br />\n香港政府(Now)＝＞港共政權"},{"pid":"11ce7c902ebd6f7d2401b82be9ba34802501